description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are seeking a part time &lt;strong&gt;Dermatology Procedure Nurse and Nurse Prescriber&lt;/strong&gt;to join the Omnes Healthcare Family; become part of a company that makes a difference.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Hillingdon and Hounslow&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;£45,000 - £50,000 depending on experience&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;3 days a week&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;em&gt;We have fully COVID compliant infection control policies in place.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Omnes Healthcare Limited are operating within the NHS to provide personalised, quality healthcare services and have been doing so since 2006. We aim to develop supportive, genuine relationships with every patient, physician, nurse and healthcare professional that we come into contact with. We believe each patient is unique and deserves treatment that is both effective, heartfelt and has a positive outcome on their well-being.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When you join us, you&#39;ll be part of something special–an innovative and rapidly growing organisation where we know that the finest patient care comes from empowering our teams to be the very best at what they do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What is the purpose of the position?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Omnes Healthcare are looking for an enthusiastic, motivated Dermatology Procedure Nurse and Nurse Prescriber who can work independently in community clinics. The purpose of the role is to assist the clinical team in the service and delivery of the dermatology service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are the key responsibilities?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The post holder will be able to undertake minor operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The post holder will be able to work independently and as a part of a wider interdisciplinary clinical team, and demonstrates excellent communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What do you need to join the Omnes Healthcare Family?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Current NMC Registration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Independent prescribing qualification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evidence of professional updating&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evidence of post-registration training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment to developing professional practice and skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience performing minor operations, punch biopsies, excisions and cryotherapy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience conducting Patient follow ups and home visits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience of managing and developing nursing teams is desirable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Omnes Healthcare will offer you in return?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;25 days holiday plus bank holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An extra day off to celebrate your birthday&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS Discount&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;And other benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Apply today if you want to make a difference.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We believe in innovation; we believe in listening to everyone; we believe in providing quality service; and we believe our employees will help us achieve our mission.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Please be aware that all communications about this vacancy will be received to you via email. Always check your mail box and junk mail folders and provide a UK mobile number if available.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
